00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:02,300
Anything!
I climb-a the highest mountain!

476
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:04,100
Down and up, up and-a down!

477
00:50:04,100 --> 00:50:07,000
I put-a my arm into the
