497
00:52:14,900 --> 00:52:16,400
I love you!

498
00:52:49,900 --> 00:52:51,000
Go away!

499
00:52:57,200 --> 00:53:01,000
Go away! I'm sure your
new partner is more important than I am.

500
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:03,900
Oh Harpo, I thought it was...

501
