Sorry, Harpo.

534
00:56:11,800 --> 00:56:13,800
I'm afraid everything isn't very much,

535
00:56:13,800 --> 00:56:16,300
without that rotten,
horrible Mike Johnson.

536
00:56:17,500 --> 00:56:19,300
